extract file to same folder(extract here)usingwinrar.

open "wii back up manager"

click add
click files
browse for this wbfs file and double click on it
tick the box on the left
click on transfer
select iso
select where you want .iso game image to go
burn .iso image using nero burning rom or whatever you like.
easy
infact this extracts straight to the .iso image,
